# RELEASE — zsh-snap-new

Version:  v1.0
Date:     2026-04-06
Platform: openSUSE Tumbleweed
Shell:    zsh 5.9+

---

## What's in this release

### Initial release
- `snap-new` — fully interactive guided snapshot creation
- Step-by-step prompts: reason, config (root/home), type (standard/important), confirmation
- Auto-detects available snapper configs — `home` prompt only shown if config exists
- `--cleanup-algorithm timeline` always set
- `important=yes` userdata protects snapshot from automatic cleanup
- Colored ANSI feedback throughout
